      "acceptanceCriteria": "QoIs (hemolysis index, wall shear stress maxima) must directly map to clinical endpoints specified in device submission.",
      "rationale": "Hemolysis index directly corresponds to plasma-free hemoglobin threshold in ISO 10993-4. Wall shear stress peaks used to identify worst-case operating point, directly supporting the regulatory decision question for the Class II CPB device."
