    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped out per ASME V&V 40 Table 4 at MRL 2. CFD hemolysis predictions demonstrate sufficient credibility to identify worst-case operating conditions for the Class II CPB device submission. Decision supports regulatory use of simulation results in lieu of additional physical testing for operating-point optimization.",
